snippet.textDisplay:
I have heard this song so many times and every time it gives me goosebumps. It's such an awesomely sang and composed song. 
Talking about the lyrics, I knew the gist of the song but never paid attention to its every line. Recently, after the cyclone Amphan in WB and its dire consequences on the poor...I went through the meaning of each and every line. OMG, salute to the lyricist. Each line has so much depth and meaning. This whole song represents the level that Coke Studio presents. Hats off guyzz!!
